metadata.name: ETH Cat
metadata.description:
The cat's home is in one of the tallest towers in the city, ETH cat is one of the richest characters in Trippy Cosmos.
There are photos of this famous person on social media showing the ETH cat alone.
Perhaps because of it's black color, it isn't often seen in the dark of night.
But he is always present in all the important scenes of the world.
And looking for a big secret!!
Join her to discover this great secret.
